Description:
A very thick fog rises in front of you. As you move forward, a tavern appears out of nowhere.

You decide to enter and then you see the tavern keeper who says to you:

"Welcome, it's good to see new faces! What brings you here, do you want a drink? If you want I can also sell you some personalized cups along with your drinks."
DescriptionAction: What do you want to do?
